<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row main">
      <!-- Start Left Side -->
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3 text-center">
        <%= image_tag @user.gravatar_url, class: 'center-block img-circle img-thumbnail img-responsive' %>
        
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item text-muted">Brandon Hay</li>
          <li class="list-group-item text-right"><%= @user.created_at.strftime('%B %e, %Y') %>
            <span class="pull-left">
              <strong>Joined</strong>
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item text-right"><%= time_ago_in_words(@user.last_sign_in_at) %> ago
            <span class="pull-left">
              <strong>Last seen</strong>
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item text-right"><%= @user.products.count %>
            <span class="pull-left">
              <strong>Products</strong>
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item text-right"><%= @user.comments.count %>
            <span class="pull-left">
              <strong>Comments</strong>
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- End Left Side -->
      <div class="clearfix visible-xs"></div>
      <!-- Start Right Side -->
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
            <!-- Start About Me -->
            <h2>About <%= @user.first_name %>:</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec vehicula lobortis felis, eget porta augue consequat et. Aliquam arcu nisi, imperdiet et consequat tincidunt, consectetur a diam. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Duis dictum libero libero, eget placerat diam porttitor molestie. Duis fermentum elementum augue, at fermentum leo rutrum vel. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Duis ut diam lorem. Sed elementum orci ac porta tempus. Nunc consectetur velit quis ornare elementum. In adipiscing tellus sit amet enim rhoncus dictum. Nunc in sapien in nunc facilisis pretium. Cras pretium tempus sem. Nunc imperdiet magna tellus.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
            <!-- End About Me -->

            <!-- Start Latest Projects -->
            <h2>Products</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <% @user.products.each do |product| %>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                  <div class="thumbnail">
                    <%= link_to image_tag(product.photo.url), controller: 'products', action: 'show', id: product %>
                    <div class="caption">
                      <h3><%= product.title %></h3>
                      <% if current_user == product.user %>
                        <p><em>You posted this product <%= time_ago_in_words(product.created_at) %> ago.</em></p>
                        <p><%= link_to t('.edit', :default => t("helpers.links.edit")),
                                    edit_product_path(product), :class => 'btn btn-default btn-xs' %>
                        <%= link_to t('.destroy', :default => t("helpers.links.destroy")),
                                    product_path(product),
                                    :method => :delete,
                                    :data => { :confirm => t('.confirm', :default => t("helpers.links.confirm", :default => 'Are you sure?')) },
                                    :class => 'btn btn-xs btn-danger' %></p>
                      <% else %>
                        <p><%= product.description %></p>
                        <p><%= link_to "Add to cart", product_path(product), class: 'btn btn-primary' %></p>
                      <% end %>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
</body>
